& [SLMPrimerProviderEvidenceContract] is the contract for provider evidence in machine-reingestible primers
  + [contract_uuid] is 6c22925d-f1de-4377-8775-b5139fc957ad
  + [slice_id] is SLM-28
  + [status] is source_implemented_policy_gated

  & [Purpose] is to keep lower-provider evidence visible in the primer
    = must: include compact provider suggestions
    = must: include provider deliberation refs for objection, answer, jury, and faculty-report evidence
    = must: preserve provider identity in compact evidence refs
    = must: keep primer output machine-reingestible
    - never: hide lower-provider disagreement behind only an aggregate wobble score

  & [CompactProviderSuggestion] is a provider evidence primer item
    + [kind] is provider_suggestion
    + [id] is ProviderSuggestion id
    + [summary] includes suggestion kind and payload
    + [refs] include target_ref and provider_id
    + [support_activation] is provider support when present

  & [CompactProviderDeliberation] is a provider deliberation primer item
    + [kind] is provider_deliberation
    + [id] is ProviderDeliberation id
    + [summary] includes status, objecting provider, and supporting provider count
    + [refs] include candidate_ref, objection refs, answer refs, jury refs, and faculty_report_refs

  & [RuntimeProjection] is slm_rust/src/primer.rs compact_evidence
    + [status] is source_complete_policy_gated
